{"tid":1631584,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(旺角)多謝車手 保姆車 響安好有用！！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T09:08:35.000Z","uid":28727,"like":95,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0e2af69c7e84e3e840d2e5d2cc76a565faf7c482","tid":1631584,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"今晚喺旺角幾個鐘都好平靜 一隻popo都無<br />\n 點知十點幾十一點就無啦啦成班出現圍捕<br />\n個陣我喺天橋 睇唔到咩事 <br />\n淨喺聽到保姆車長響安<br />\n一望落去就見到有一大班popo<br />\n真喺多謝個班車手<br />\n宜家啲狗唔聲唔聲咁出現<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 車手見到 長響安真喺好有用！！！ </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 車手見到 長響安真喺好有用！！！ </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 車手見到 長響安真喺好有用！！！ </span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔沉常咁長響安 提大家要走<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>傳開去！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申發夢見到"},{"pid":"e45ff48962aec3c8b21b95c457d1aff1064e551f","tid":1631584,"uid":75959,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"dbe1aca2c7d7fe64687d07991d4e2bbfbe8cb689","tid":1631584,"uid":28727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人！反抗！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警死全家</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7cf10e7e620a94a3666a2b1b9abf57ff726e6574","tid":1631584,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9fb989b376a15451247bb88024f20fe777d70db","tid":1631584,"uid":57338,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"而家好多狗車閃燈唔響"},{"pid":"9478c2d95f91ad5733b32d14fbcba01ab111e48a","tid":1631584,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:02:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf5396a61ea38e0d654da09766e975f8d37e1f81","tid":1631584,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:02:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9770af18173ceea57ad1d0fc5bf32287c625b83","tid":1631584,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631278</a>"},{"pid":"a815f4d0893ca1887b8a3d431ce279ffc1b87672","tid":1631584,"uid":191706,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:03:30.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係有建設嘅post 唔好再去內控啦"},{"pid":"6a34a7f820ca61a21c6fc